➜北京姑娘继承50㎡二环胡同房，地面铺镜子、浴厕全透明：一个人住太爽
http://www.sohu.com/a/419104372_157906	55788
<p class="ql-align-center"><iframe width="500" height="300" scrolling="no" frameborder="0" border="0" allowfullscreen="true" src="//tv.sohu.com/s/sohuplayer/iplay.html?bid=215194795&amp;vars=%5B%5B%22showRecommend%22%2C0%5D%5D&amp;disablePlaylist=true&amp;mute=1&amp;autoplay=false"></iframe></p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p1.itc.cn/images01/20200917/bb71f1cc216044cca7ad6ee65b3151d9.jpeg" style="user-select: auto;" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>90后姑娘刘天萌，</p>
<p>大学以前都生活在北京。</p>
<p>家人在鼓楼边的宝钞胡同里</p>
<p>给她留了栋老房子，</p>
<p>2018年她留学回来，</p>
<p>决心要做个彻底的改造，</p>
<p>独立在这里生活。</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p7.itc.cn/images01/20200917/26a957406f7243f1bbd0fa0d716b311c.gif" style="user-select: auto;" max-width="600" /></p>
<p>改造后的老房小院是个镜面空间</p>
<p class="ql-align-center"><img src="http://p2.itc.cn/images01/20200917/c294ddef064e40bda1c4095b2c5f2ed7.gif" style="user-select: auto;" max-width="600" /></p>            <div class="lookall-box">
